transcript: - It's actually right here beside me. The new Mac Studio with the M2 Ultra Chip. (breathes deeply) I'm sweating. The configuration that I have here in the studio is an M2 Ultra with a 24-core CPU, 76-core GPU, and a 128 gigs of memory with four terabytes of storage. Let's see if I can put 22 streams of 8K into an 8K timeline. This is running so smooth and this is all ProRes 8K.
